# Governs the source upload for `gcloud run deploy --source .` / Cloud Build.
# IMPORTANT: the mere existence of this file stops gcloud from falling back to
# .gitignore — which excludes data/processed & data/raw and would ship an empty
# demo dataset (claims/citations 404). Keep those here.
.git/
.gitignore
.gitattributes
.venv/
**/__pycache__/
**/*.pyc
.pytest_cache/
tests/
docs/
*.md
.env
.env.example
.claude/
node_modules/
frontend/node_modules/
frontend/dist/
docker-compose.yml

# Pre-loaded demo data IS required (Dockerfile `COPY data/` ships it):
#   - data/processed/  -> claims.json + per-document JSON (citation text source)
#   - data/raw/SYN-*.pdf -> synthetic NVDA call pages for the citation viewer
# Only the bulky real-filing HTML is dropped: real-filing citations render from
# the processed JSON, and live processing re-fetches raw filings at runtime.
data/raw/*.html
